name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $destination
desc: Returns: The destination application which the message is intended for.

name: $adddestination
desc: The destination application which the message is intended for.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The destination application which the message is intended for.

name: $sender
desc: Returns: Identifies the sending system to allow the use of a trust relationship.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies the sending system to allow the use of a trust relationship.

name: $enterer
desc: Returns: The person or device that performed the data entry leading to this message. When there is more than one candidate, pick the most proximal to the message. Can provide other enterers in extensions.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The person or device that performed the data entry leading to this message. When there is more than one candidate, pick the most proximal to the message. Can provide other enterers in extensions.

name: $author
desc: Returns: The logical author of the message - the person or device that decided the described event should happen. When there is more than one candidate, pick the most proximal to the MessageHeader. Can provide other authors in extensions.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The logical author of the message - the person or device that decided the described event should happen. When there is more than one candidate, pick the most proximal to the MessageHeader. Can provide other authors in extensions.

name: $source
desc: Returns: The source application from which this message originated.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The source application from which this message originated.

name: $responsible
desc: Returns: The person or organization that accepts overall responsibility for the contents of the message. The implication is that the message event happened under the policies of the responsible party.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The person or organization that accepts overall responsibility for the contents of the message. The implication is that the message event happened under the policies of the responsible party.

name: $reason
desc: Returns: Coded indication of the cause for the event - indicates  a reason for the occurrence of the event that is a focus of this message.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Coded indication of the cause for the event - indicates  a reason for the occurrence of the event that is a focus of this message.

name: $response
desc: Returns: Information about the message that this message is a response to.  Only present if this message is a response.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Information about the message that this message is a response to.  Only present if this message is a response.

name: $focus
desc: Returns: The actual data of the message - a reference to the root/focus class of the event.

name: $addfocus
desc: The actual data of the message - a reference to the root/focus class of the event.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The actual data of the message - a reference to the root/focus class of the event.

name: $definition
desc: Returns: Permanent link to the MessageDefinition for this message.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Permanent link to the MessageDefinition for this message.
